{"tid":1519611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831出唔出去？","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:29:52.000Z","uid":61672,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"550007385cb70d1dd056c1999b493f4e837262e7","tid":1519611,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:20:48.000Z","msg":"轉載～<br />\n<br />\n平時和理非的立場新聞，鼓勵你衝，<br />\n連最阻人衝的張超雄也響應。<br />\n830無理地拘捕不同派別的反對派人士，<br />\n又用言語刺激說你「行街也犯法」。<br />\n不怕一萬，至怕萬一，似是請君入甕，誘捕勇武，泛民收網，既可滅政敵，又有光環，預備接下來的選舉。<br />\n<br />\n記住我們暫時已夠彈藥，在美國復會前不需再犯險，要打，等美國通過法案後。這不是叫你無了期收手，不是叫你妥協，是擇日再打的戰略。第二次世界大戰，冬天時也要停火養兵的。好好練兵，等待復出之時，到時就是血債血償了，明日任由和理非慢慢玩吧。要打，先打那班到美國閉門會議代表港人的仆街，並要盡用之前的抗爭成果，宣傳到美國。<br />\n<br />\n保重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f29ea5abb0b4722bb3bec5ea41dace31ff1743","tid":1519611,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43fb691b85a9af0d5246192e57086419bf7348ea","tid":1519611,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"698b4ad8e5d9813667102c5b576b4e3dd9c09a21","tid":1519611,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc1e8fc8c61365c733f6a1afe2610153c3be5e2f","tid":1519611,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39d08b4a7147cf1e0dd689c9e6f13e1e3d4cfc9a","tid":1519611,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9b8fdee597a94263765